title: WTF | Watch: This horrible elevator chime is going viral for all the right/wrong reasons
text:
Dubbed 'The World's Most Pathetic Elevator Chime', this lift on the 10th floor of the Novotel Hotel in Melbourne, Australia has gone viral for sounding like the most hungover, sad and/or dying lift ever heard. It's a feeling we can all relate to.
We think it's a bit like a dying giraffe , or that it's saying its own version of 'Shurrup yew ye TICK' .
What do you think it sounds like?
Via YouTube
